c_n = \sqrt1 + \sqrt2 + \cdots + \sqrt{n}
c_n \sim \dfrac23 {n^{3/2}} + \dfrac12 {n^{1/2}} + \dfrac1{24} \cdot \dfrac1{n^{1/2}}
b_n = \sum_{k=1}^n (-1)^{k+1} \sqrt{k}
